---
title: Hoisin Style Beef with pak choi and green beans
description: The succulent beef in this recipe is cooked in a special blend of spices and coated with sticky, sweet, and salty hoisin sauce for added flavour. Fragrant jasmine rice adds a filling factor to the dish.
